          "nl": "Upload PV data: [[power]]Watt, [[meter]]kWh vandaag tot nu."
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Upload the current values of the solar panels. You can enter one or both values. Use the special WHEN card to prevent sending too often. Note that the energy (kWh) should contain the daily value.",
